HEADWORD: Lungfish
<hw>Lung"fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any fish belonging to the Dipnoi; -- so called because they have
both lungs and gills.</def>⟦br⟧
